OL,3,CMike Phillips banned for drink-driving
OL,4,Cafter being three times limit
OL,6,FFormer Wales rugby star Mike Phillips
OL,7,Fhas been banned from the road for two
OL,8,Fyears after pleading guilty to drink-
OL,9,Fdriving.
OL,11,FThe ex-scrum-half, who won 99
OL,12,Finternational caps for Wales and the
OL,13,FBritish & Irish Lions, was found to be
OL,14,Fthree times over the legal limit when
OL,15,Fhe was arrested in Llanwrtyd Wells on
OL,16,FJuly 7.
OL,18,FA breathalyser recorded a reading of
OL,19,F108mcg of alcohol per 100ml of breath
OL,20,Fwith the legal limit being 35mcg.
