OL,3,CMike Phillips banned for drink-driving
OL,4,Cafter being three times limit
OL,6,FPhillips' case was heard at
OL,7,FLlandrindod Wells Magistrates' Court
OL,8,Fon Wednesday, July 31, with the 41-
OL,9,Fyear-old ` who lives in Dubai `
OL,10,Fpleading guilty to drink-driving.
OL,12,FHe gave his full name as William Mike
OL,13,FPhillips and provided an address at
OL,14,FStation Road, St Clears,
OL,15,FCarmarthenshire. The court heard that
OL,16,Fhe had been driving an Audi A4 at the
OL,17,Ftime of the offence.
