OL,3,CMike Phillips banned for drink-driving
OL,4,Cafter being three times limit
OL,6,FFollowing his guilty plea magistrates
OL,7,Fbanned the former Scarlets, Cardiff,
OL,8,Fand Ospreys back from driving for 25
OL,9,Fmonths. However he can reduce this by
OL,10,Fcompleting a drink-driving awareness
OL,11,Fcourse.
OL,13,FPhillips was also fined #1,153 while
OL,14,Fhe must also pay a #461 surcharge and
OL,15,F#85 in costs.
